<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/24868012">有哪些歌词叙事性很强的歌曲？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2129178" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">想听一些有故事，有感悟，当然旋律也要好听的歌曲。求推荐。Thx</div>


</div>
